FBIS4-62257 "drsov093_c_94001" FBIS-SOV-94-093 Daily Report 12 May 1994 Federal Assembly Chernomyrdin Creates Government Standing Conference Body Chernomyrdin Creates Government Standing Conference Body LD1205135594 Moscow Mayak Radio Network in Russian 1100 GMT 12 May 94 LD1205135594 Moscow Mayak Radio Network Russian BFN [Text] Prime Minister Viktor Chernomyrdin has signed a decision on setting up a standing working conference of the Russian Federation Government. It is the aim of the conference to enhance cooperation between the Government and the executive authorities of the Russian Federation's constituent parts, and to ensure that decisions on issues concerning the implementation of economic reforms and regional, social, and economic development are agreed upon in advance.
